\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces The complete system architecture of SB-GRPO. The Heuristic Confidence Gate ($\Gamma $) dynamically routes uniform batches to the Advantage Calibration module (Path A) to prevent advantage vanishing. For mixed batches (Path B), the framework applies Multi-Layer Reflection and Semantic Error Profiling (SEP) to extract the Top Error Cluster ($C_{top}$), forming a Static Balanced Batch optimized by an Entropy-Aware Loss Scaling factor ($\lambda $).}}{4}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{1}{4}{The complete system architecture of SB-GRPO. The Heuristic Confidence Gate ($\Gamma $) dynamically routes uniform batches to the Advantage Calibration module (Path A) to prevent advantage vanishing. For mixed batches (Path B), the framework applies Multi-Layer Reflection and Semantic Error Profiling (SEP) to extract the Top Error Cluster ($C_{top}$), forming a Static Balanced Batch optimized by an Entropy-Aware Loss Scaling factor ($\lambda $)}{figure.1}{}}
