\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Absolute performance gains of SB-GRPO on MATH sub-categories. \textbf  {Top:} Compared to M-GRPO, where significant improvements in \textit  {Intermediate Algebra} (+4.88\%) and \textit  {Precalculus} (+5.68\%) demonstrate the effectiveness of semantic balancing in complex reasoning. \textbf  {Bottom:} Compared to Vanilla GRPO, highlighting the massive broad-spectrum improvements achieved by the reflection mechanism.}}{10}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
